'''Géraldine Fleitcher''' was a [[Gender/Legends|female]] born around [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]]. She was a scoop-hungry reporter for the [[Freedom Galactic News]] with something to prove; namely, her independence from her father, the [[Coruscant Galactic Media]]'s mogul [[Graham Fleitcher]]. Her quarrelsome character disguised the fact that she was the brains of Freedom Galactic News.

